## 📊 Workflow D — Provider Dashboard

- [ ] As a provider, I land on the **Dashboard tab** by default when opening the app
- [ ] As a provider, I can see my **today's job queue, earnings snapshot, and Shines rating summary**
- [ ] As a provider, jobs awaiting approval show a **2-hour countdown timer** prominently
- [ ] As a provider, I can tap the **Earnings card** and see weekly and monthly breakdowns
- [ ] As a provider, I can see **net earnings after platform fee deduction**, with pending payouts highlighted separately
- [ ] As a provider, I can tap **Schedule** and view a calendar with confirmed bookings and blocked dates
- [ ] As a provider, I can **tap a date to mark it as unavailable**, blocking new booking requests for that day
- [ ] As a provider, I can set **recurring unavailability** (e.g. every Sunday)
- [ ] As a provider, I can see my **Gear score breakdown (4 dimensions), Kudos badge wall, and 30-day rating trend** on my dashboard

