## 🎁 Workflow I — Gift Cards & Promo Codes

- [ ] As a customer, I can navigate to **More > Gift Cards** and see my existing card balance
- [ ] As a customer, I can purchase a gift card in **$25, $50, $100, or custom** amounts
- [ ] As a customer, the recipient receives a **branded email with a redemption code**
- [ ] As a customer, **gift cards never expire** (Virginia gift card law compliance)
- [ ] As a customer, I can tap **Add Promo Code** at checkout and apply a valid code
- [ ] As a customer, **invalid codes return an error** before payment confirmation
- [ ] As a customer, the **discount is displayed** on the review screen before I confirm
- [ ] As a customer, **single-use codes are invalidated** immediately upon redemption
- [ ] Promo codes support **flat dollar off, percentage off, and free service** types

---

## 👥 Workflow J — Referral Program

- [ ] As a user, I can navigate to **More > Refer a Friend** and see my unique referral code
- [ ] As a user, I can see **total referrals sent and total credits earned**, with pending credits shown separately
- [ ] As a user, I can tap **Share** and a native share sheet opens with a pre-populated message and unique referral link
- [ ] As a user, I can see the status of each referral: **Signed Up, First Booking Pending, Credit Earned**
- [ ] As a referrer, I receive a **$10 credit** when the referred user completes and pays for their first booking
- [ ] As a referred user, I also receive a **$10 credit** on my first completed booking
- [ ] As a user, referral credits are **applied as promo codes** at checkout via Workflow I
- [ ] Referral credits have a **12-month expiry** and are non-transferable

