## 🔁 Workflow K — Recurring Subscriptions *(Phase 2 — Deferred)*

- [ ] *(Deferred)* As a customer, I can set up a recurring schedule with **weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly** cadence
- [ ] *(Deferred)* As a customer, I can **pause, modify, or cancel** a recurring subscription from the Subscription Dashboard
- [ ] *(Deferred)* As a customer, I can cancel a recurring schedule with **48 hours notice** before the next booking

