## 🛠️ Workflow L — Admin Panel

- [x] As an admin, I can log in to the **desktop web portal** (1280px minimum width)  _(magic-link; /admin)_
- [ ] As an admin, I can see a KPI overview: **GMV, active providers, open disputes, and NPS** (refreshes every 5 min)
- [~] As an admin, I can **search and filter providers** and take actions: Approve, Suspend, Flag for Review  _(search + Approve/Reject done; Suspend/Flag are follow-ups)_
- [x] As an admin, I can **approve or reject a provider** with a reason code, and an approval email is triggered to the provider within 60 seconds  _(admin-review-provider Edge Fn + Resend)_
- [~] As an admin, I can **review insurance certificates** and manually approve or reject them  _(insurance_status shown + overall approve/reject; in-panel signed-URL cert preview is a follow-up — bucket is service-role only)_
- [ ] As an admin, I can open a dispute and view **booking details, message thread, and before/after photos**
- [ ] As an admin, I can **issue full or partial refunds**, ban users, or send warnings — all audit-logged with my name and timestamp
- [ ] As an admin, I can **create promo codes** with fields for type, value, expiry, max redemptions, and user segment
- [ ] As an admin, I can view **GMV, bookings, and provider earnings** over a selected date range, exportable as CSV
- [ ] As an admin, I can **force-cancel any booking** with full or partial refund
- [ ] Role-based access is enforced: **Admin (full), Support (disputes/refunds only), Finance (payouts/analytics only)**

