## 💸 Workflow M — Provider Payout & Tax

- [ ] As a provider, I can navigate to **More > Payout Settings** and see my linked bank account and payout schedule
- [ ] As a provider, I can **add a bank account** via Stripe's secure input (Stabl never stores raw bank details)
- [ ] As a provider, I can view **payout history** with per-booking breakdown (gross, fee, net, transfer date)
- [ ] As a provider, I can **download my 1099-K** for the applicable tax year (generated if I earn > $600/year)
- [ ] As a provider below the threshold, I still receive an **annual earnings summary**
- [ ] As a provider, my **payout is blocked** until Stripe Connect onboarding is fully complete
- [ ] As a provider in the Founding Program, I am on **0% platform fee** for 3 months, auto-converting to 3% after

