## 🛒 Workflow N — Provider Service Setup

- [ ] As a provider, I can navigate to the **Services tab** and see an empty state prompting me to add my first service
- [ ] As a provider, I can browse the **Stabl platform service catalog** and add services
- [ ] As a provider, I can **edit description, price, and estimated duration** for each service (price and duration required)
- [ ] As a provider, I can add up to **3 custom services** (subject to moderation before approval)
- [ ] As a provider, custom services are **not searchable platform-wide** — only discoverable on my profile
- [ ] As a provider, I can tap **Preview** to see the exact customer-facing version of my service listing
- [ ] As a provider, I can tap **Publish** and my service menu goes live immediately in search
- [ ] As a provider, I can **toggle services on/off** without deleting them from my menu